data.description: Contract Pending. Beautiful house, well care in a quit neighborhood, close to shopping, schools, parks and much more services. 3 Bedrooms and one full bath in the mainfloor, plus an apartment in the basement with 2 Non-conforming bedrooms, kitchinette and 3/4 bathroom, perfect for an extra income source. Light fixtures, wood flooring, plenty of space in the backyard, fully fence, This house is the last one on the left before the paved road ends, which adds total privacy to the house. Don't miss this amazing opportunity!!
